  "2 - Conditions to activate functions": {
   "width": 12180,
   "height": 3300,
   "color": "rgb(199,209,254)",
   "labels": [
    {
     "text": "To write DID it is necessary to have no assist: IGN ON, engine stopped, CAN vehicule speed valide <3km/h. ECU reset or IGNOFF/ON is necessary if assistance has been raised already.",
